snippet: Betaworks, a technology incubator in New York, has purchased Digg, a social news site that has slowly lost steam amid the rise of services like Twitter and Facebook.
abstract: Betaworks, a technology incubator in New York, has purchased Digg, a social news site that has slowly lost steam amid the rise of services like Twitter and Facebook.

headline.main: Betaworks Buys What's Left of Social News Site Digg
